For complete feature support upgrade to Tasmota development release [2c6df2b](https://github.com/arendst/Sonoff-Tasmota/commit/2c6df2b86b9a7dfc986a06e9d4c58918e6bb61a4) from April 15th 2019 or up.

Follow the [discussion](https://github.com/arendst/Sonoff-Tasmota/issues/5592) for possible issues and troubleshooting.
